			<item>
				<title>Finatra 1.6.0 Released</title>
				<description>&lt;h3&gt;Last release for 1.x.x and Scala 2.9&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
As we prepare for the upcoming 2.x.x release, this will be the last 1.x.x release
and also the last release to be published for scala 2.9.x.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;New Finatra and Maintainer!&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
I&amp;#39;m happy to announce that &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/scosenza&quot;&gt;Steve Cosenza&lt;/a&gt; will be
taking over the project for the 2.x.x release and beyond. We&amp;#39;re excited to release
the next major iteration of Finatra and share everything we&amp;#39;ve learned using it in
production at &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt; over the course of a year.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Changelog&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/d90c77dbd09fb74abacb437258f1d60bf92efd8d&quot;&gt;d90c77&lt;/a&gt; Can use ChannelBuffer&amp;#39;s as Response&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/d73cbbf644f58ed1dd756f186b1e272e31b0ae39&quot;&gt;d73cbb&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/8192716f00ae513358d1210645e4e47352be8e48&quot;&gt;819271&lt;/a&gt; Fix controller-specific ErrorHandler&amp;#39;s&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/129184a90f4255a97e2983407b324747f8c218e4&quot;&gt;129184&lt;/a&gt; Fixed Heroku Deployments&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/bpfoster/finatra/commit/04b5cbb9e71488d590eab76cffcc284685cbaa47&quot;&gt;04b5cb&lt;/a&gt; 2 Way SSL support&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/fcce1669c3b2e5a14d7a242db64b226f8be3b73b&quot;&gt;fcce16&lt;/a&gt; Quieter errors in the logs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/33b1063d4c59d8ea82dc37f176484cde64f26bc8&quot;&gt;33b106&lt;/a&gt; Asset Directory browser! set com.twitter.finatra.showDirectories=true to enable&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/2edd33df0bd5a5be4d6161b7c8bd53954593939f&quot;&gt;2edd33&lt;/a&gt; Clean up build files, lock to twitter-server 1.7.3&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/982703ab79900d6a0e2ab7d6ff039accf0723979&quot;&gt;982703&lt;/a&gt; Remove scalatest dependency from jar, must now depend on it yourself&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4&gt;SBT&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-scala&quot; data-lang=&quot;scala&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;com.twitter&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;%%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;finatra&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;1.6.0&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Maven&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-xml&quot; data-lang=&quot;xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;com.twitter&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;finatra_2.10&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;1.6.0&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 09 Jan 2015 03:00:00 -0800</pubDate>
